<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>There is a problem with the description of getTranslation method (with regard to 'LanguageToTerritory' type).
The documentation says that it returns a list of territories' names when in fact it returns a list of languages.</p>

<p>In the file Zend_Locale-Functions.xml
lines 1420-1426 say: "(...) When a language is used in multiple territories then these territories are separated with a whitespace character"
it should be: "(...) When a territory uses multiple languages then these languages are separated with a whitespace character"</p>

    </div>
